  dialogueVariations:
  - lines:
    - '"Hello? Is this the support line for that... Foodika app?"'
    - '"I''m trying to find a decent local restaurant, but the map just keeps spinning."'
    - '"Oh, wait. Never mind. I forgot to turn my location on. Sorry to bother you."'
  - lines:
    - '"Hi, yes, I received a missed call from this number?"'
    - '"No? Are you sure? It''s showing up right here on my caller ID."'
    - '"Well, alright then. Have a good night, I guess."'
  - lines:
    - '"Good evening. I''m calling to update my billing address on file."'
    - '"Actually, wait... I think my wife already did it this morning."'
    - '"Let me just check... yes, she did. My mistake. Thank you for your time."'
